com.viaoa.ds.objectcache

Class ObjectCacheIterator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.ds.objectcache.ObjectCacheIterator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OADataSourceIterator, Iterator

    public class ObjectCacheIterator<T>
extends Object
implements OADataSourceIterator
    Used to find and filter objects in OAObjectCache. Note, all queries require that a non-null Filter be used. If filter is null, then no results will be returned.

    vvia
